benchmark.py:
  Run a program with memory and runtime bounds and log file support.
  Can be used as a module or as a standalone script.

repository.py:
  Module for querying the planning task database (list domain, list problems
  in domain, suggest file names for log files, etc.).

solver.py:
  Run the three-phase causal graph planner. Phases can be executed separately
  or in sequence. Solve one task, all tasks in one domain, or all tasks in the
  database.
  Can be used as a module or as a standalone script.

solve-first.py:
  Sample script which shows how solver.py can be used as a module.
  Solve the first task of each domain in the task database.

run-all-planners.py:
  Script for running the other planners on all tasks in the database.
